                <head>Inhabitants of Oftringen</head>
                <note rend="inline" rendition="#center" type="source">[Translation.]</note>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Oftringen</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-05-30">
                        <hi rend="italic">May</hi> 30, 1865</date>.</dateline>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="italic">To the Editor of the Bund, in Berne:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>We hereby respectfully request you to insert the enclosed communication in your
                    estimable paper. Hoping you will oblige us with such a slight favor, we remain,
                    yours, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>LANG HUSSY, </signed>
                    <hi rend="italic">Councellor</hi>.</closer>
                <frus:attachment>
                    <head rendition="#center">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">expression of sympathy for the american
                        union</hi>.</head>
                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“On motion of Mr. Lang Hussy, at a meeting of many citizens of Oftringen,
                            just after the state elections, it was unanimously resolved to approve
                            of the Swiss address of sympathy and condolence to the American
                            Union.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </frus:attachment>
            </div>
        </body>
